.TH COMMAND * 2014-04-08 "SequoiaDB" "Sequoiadb sdb's Manual"
.ad l.ll 72.ce 1000
\fBdb.execUpdate()\fR
.ce 0
.sp 2

.SH "NAME"

.sp 2
execUpdate - SQL execution of other statements.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"

.sp 2

.sp 2

.sp 2
db.execUpdate(\fB<other sql>\fR)
.SH "CATEGORY"

.sp 2

.sp 2
Sequoiadb
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

.sp 2
SQL execution of other statements.
.SH "Examples"

.sp 2
The collection "my.my" insert a new record.
.sp 2
db.execUpdate("insert into my.my(name,age) values('zhangshang', 30) ")